  Source:
    Title: The Book of Hours
    Locus: I 4
  Locus:
    Daily: December 19
Format: Verse
Title: Piously We Produce
---
Piously we produce our images of you
till they stand around you like a thousand walls.

And when our hearts would simply open,
our fervent hands hide you.
